propClasses: Override or extend the styles applied to the component.
propDelay: Adds a transition delay, to allow a series of SpeedDialActions to be animated.
propIcon: The Icon to display in the SpeedDial Fab.
propId:
This prop is used to help implement the accessibility logic.
If you don't provide this prop. It falls back to a randomly generated id.
propTooltipOpen: Make the tooltip always visible when the SpeedDial is open.
propTooltipTitle: Label to display in the tooltip.
stylesFab: Styles applied to the Fab component.
stylesFabClosed: Styles applied to the Fab component if `open={false}`.
stylesStaticTooltip: Styles applied to the root element if `tooltipOpen={true}`.
stylesStaticTooltipClosed: Styles applied to the root element if `tooltipOpen={true}` and `open={false}`.
stylesStaticTooltipLabel: Styles applied to the static tooltip label if `tooltipOpen={true}`.
stylesTooltipPlacementLeft: Styles applied to the root if `tooltipOpen={true}` and `tooltipPlacement="left"``
stylesTooltipPlacementRight: Styles applied to the root if `tooltipOpen={true}` and `tooltipPlacement="right"``
